  "detailed_description": "Q. What kind of game is this?<br><br>A. This is a pixel tower defense shooting game, where the player is a hero who helps our camp defeat powerful and crazy monsters!<br><br>TOWER<br>As long as there is open space, you can freely arrange defense towers to block the monster's attack<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2723170/extras/7c3e3d688cfa6d0c1a38ab0a5d37e112.avif?t=1707486056\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>reinforce<br>In some levels, players will receive regular support from friendly NPCs to defeat monsters and achieve victory together<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2723170/extras/c65778d46a8ea00eb3885b215e8c82c8.avif?t=1707486056\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>transition<br>Each level has its own unique features. Starting from level 5, the game will usher in a new gameplay of escorting, attacking, and annihilating. At the same time, the difficulty of the game will also increase accordingly<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2723170/extras/a1b6fd94181263cc86095fe4a9e339f7.avif?t=1707486056\" width=600 height=336 /></span>",
